headline: Graco Inc. (GGG) Beats Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Graco (GGG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 2.94% and 0.66%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
